    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/17b6befebbd29b7ac71d43924e20eb8b.poster.avif?t=1683035360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/17b6befebbd29b7ac71d43924e20eb8b.webm?t=1683035360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/17b6befebbd29b7ac71d43924e20eb8b.mp4?t=1683035360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Midnight Shift is a first-person sim were the player takes the role of a gas station attendant working the midnight shift.   The player will need to perform standard tasks and attend the to the costumers needs.  Everything will seem fine until you start receiving harassment calls and a stranger starts stocking you.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/4d9d612a879b52899dc61b4e63c5c015.poster.avif?t=1683035360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/4d9d612a879b52899dc61b4e63c5c015.webm?t=1683035360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/4d9d612a879b52899dc61b4e63c5c015.mp4?t=1683035360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>SYNOPSIS:</strong><br>Although you are having car problems; you make it to work on time.  Your midnight shift starts like any other night.  You clock in and take care of your routine tasks all while attending customers.  Everything seems fine, until a particular set of events start to unravel, and you are faced with what can only be described as a nightmare.<br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br>First-Person View<br>Keyboard &amp; Mouse Controls<br>Multiple Camera Filters<br>Interactive Objects<br>Creepy environment<br>Hair-raising chase<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/7f2bb9fb87a179105326faf351803d72.poster.avif?t=1683035360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/7f2bb9fb87a179105326faf351803d72.webm?t=1683035360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395260/extras/7f2bb9fb87a179105326faf351803d72.mp4?t=1683035360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FOR BEST EXPERIENCE:</strong><br>Use headphones<br>Play in the dark",
